    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f1f5f9; /* slate-100, professional neutral background */
            color: #0f172a; /* slate-900 */
        }

        /* 覆盖滚动条样式，严肃内敛 */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #e2e8f0; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #64748b; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #475569; }

        .glass-panel {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
        }

        .chart-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            height: 350px;
            max-height: 400px;
        }

        /* 交互卡片悬浮效果 */
        .interactive-card {
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .interactive-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
            border-color: #3b82f6;
        }

        /* 标签页高亮状态 */
        .tab-active {
            background-color: #1e293b; /* slate-800 */
            color: #ffffff !important;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        /* 密级标识 */
        .classification-badge {
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                45deg,
                #ef4444,
                #ef4444 10px,
                #dc2626 10px,
                #dc2626 20px
            );
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased leading-relaxed">

    <!-- Chosen Palette: Slate (900/800) for authority, Red (600/500) for urgent threats, Blue (600/100) for information, Emerald for secure status. Represents a serious National Security Agency briefing interface. -->
    
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: 
         1. Fixed Top Nav: Quick access to intelligence sections.
         2. Executive Summary: High-level overview with classification markings to set the tone.
         3. Section 1: Threat Assessment (Quantum & qLDPC) - Uses the Chart.js timeline and critique of academic claims to provide NSA with realistic threat timelines.
         4. Section 2: Blast Radius - Visual grid showing exactly which national assets are vulnerable (Asymmetric vs Symmetric).
         5. Section 3: Defense Solutions (PQC vs QKD/QRNG) - NEW SECTION. Uses an interactive comparative layout to evaluate physics-based vs math-based defenses, addressing NSA's specific infrastructure concerns.
         6. Section 4: Strategic Directives - Actionable, policy-level recommendations for NSA deployment. -->

    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
         - Threat Timeline: Chart.js Bar Chart (Log Scale). Goal: Show the immense gap between current tech and RSA-breaking tech, filtering out academic hype.
         - Vulnerability Grid: DOM Cards with status indicators. Goal: Quick triage of cryptographic primitives.
         - Defense Matrix: Interactive CSS/JS flex layout. Goal: Compare QKD, QRNG, and PQC directly. Interaction: Clicking expands detailed pros/cons/NSA deployment advice. Justification: Executive decision-makers need side-by-side comparative analysis of infrastructure costs vs theoretical security.
         CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. All visuals are HTML/CSS or Chart.js Canvas. -->

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-14">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <span class="text-red-500 text-xl">🛡️</span>
                    <span class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-widest">国家安全局战略内参</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-6">
                    <a href="#threat-intel" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition">威胁研判</a>
                    <a href="#asset-vuln" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition">资产脆弱性</a>
                    <a href="#defense-matrix" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition">防御技术矩阵</a>
                    <a href="#directives" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition">行动指令</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="pt-20 pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-12">

        <!-- Executive Summary Header -->
        <header class="glass-panel p-8 mt-4 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 classification-badge"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
                        后量子时代国家密码基础设施安全评估
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2 font-mono text-sm">编号: NSA-QRA-2026-04 | 状态: 供高层决策参考</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 border border-red-200 px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold text-sm">
                    绝密 / TOP SECRET
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-50 border-l-4 border-slate-800 p-5 rounded-r-lg text-slate-700 text-justify leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-slate-900">核心摘要：</strong> 
                随着量子计算（特别是容错量子纠错如qLDPC架构）的学术宣称不断涌现，评估其对现行RSA/ECC公钥体系的真实威胁刻不容缓。本报告穿透学术界的乐观预测，为国家安全局提供客观的<strong>破解时间线研判</strong>。同时，针对下一代国家级加密网络的建设，系统性评估了<strong>后量子密码（PQC）</strong>与<strong>量子密码（QKD/QRNG）</strong>的战略优劣势，为我国关键信息基础设施的换代提供决策依据。
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Section 1: Threat Intelligence (qLDPC & RSA) -->
        <section id="threat-intel" class="scroll-mt-20">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="bg-slate-900 text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mr-3 text-sm">1</span>
                威胁时间线研判：学术宣称与工程现实的鸿沟
            </h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <!-- Qubit Scaling Chart -->
                <div class="glass-panel p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">破解RSA-2048所需物理资源预估 (对数坐标)</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">需警惕文献中对“qLDPC大幅降低资源”的过度解读</p>
                    <div class="chart-container">
                        <canvas id="qubitChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-50 p-3 rounded">
                        数据研判：即便采用最激进的qLDPC架构理论，距破解RSA仍有百倍以上的物理比特数量级差距。
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Academic Critique (qLDPC reality) -->
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="glass-panel p-6 bg-slate-900 text-white">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-400">情报纠偏：qLDPC的“逻辑门悖论”</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 text-justify">
                            近期大量文献宣称qLDPC（量子低密度奇偶校验码）可将破解RSA所需的物理比特数降低90%以上。<strong>经我局技术委员会审查，此推论存在重大工程缺陷。</strong>
                        </p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-red-500 mr-2">⚠️</span>
                                <div>
                                    <strong class="text-white">缺少普适逻辑门操作：</strong> 根据Eastin-Knill定理，qLDPC无法以容错方式横向执行连续逻辑门。文献中展示的极低资源开销，往往<strong>直接假设了理想的逻辑门</strong>，这在运行Shor算法（需要海量非Clifford门）时是致命的盲区。
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-red-500 mr-2">⚠️</span>
                                <div>
                                    <strong class="text-white">硬件连通性灾难：</strong> qLDPC要求物理量子比特进行复杂的长程交叉连接，在现有的超导或自旋量子芯片上强行布线会导致灾难性的串扰噪声（Crosstalk）。
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300">
                            👉 研判结论：真正能运行Shor算法的容错量子计算机，在10-15年内仍属极低概率事件。但必须防范敌对势力的 "现在收集，未来解密" (SNDL) 战略。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2: Vulnerability -->
        <section id="asset-vuln" class="scroll-mt-20">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="bg-slate-900 text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mr-3 text-sm">2</span>
                国家密码资产脆弱性矩阵
            </h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="glass-panel p-6 border-t-4 border-red-600">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">非对称密码体制</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold">全线崩溃 (Shor算法)</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">涵盖：RSA, ECC (SM2), Diffie-Hellman</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-50 p-2 rounded"><strong>国安风险：</strong> 支撑目前政务网数字签名、密钥协商的核心机制。历史截获的高密级通信流量面临彻底暴露风险。</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-panel p-6 border-t-4 border-amber-500">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">对称密码体制</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold">安全降级 (Grover算法)</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">涵盖：AES, SM4, ChaCha20</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-50 p-2 rounded"><strong>国安风险：</strong> 量子搜索可提供二次加速。AES-128的有效强度降至2^64，不再安全。<strong>必须全面强制升级至AES-256或SM4-256。</strong></p>
                </div>

                <div class="glass-panel p-6 border-t-4 border-emerald-600">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">哈希算法</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold">抗量子安全</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">涵盖：SHA-256, SHA-3, SM3</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-50 p-2 rounded"><strong>国安风险：</strong> 量子计算对寻找哈希碰撞的加速极小。现有256位以上的哈希算法在后量子时代依然坚如磐石，无需更换。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3: Defense Solutions (PQC vs QKD) -->
        <section id="defense-matrix" class="scroll-mt-20">
            <div class="mb-6 flex justify-between items-end">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center">
                    <span class="bg-slate-900 text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mr-3 text-sm">3</span>
                    防御技术矩阵：后量子密码 (PQC) vs 量子加密 (QKD/QRNG)
                </h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">针对国家级网络的换代升级，必须在“基于数学困难的PQC”与“基于物理定律的量子加密”之间做出战略抉择。点击下方分类查看我局深度评估。</p>

            <!-- Interactive Tab Navigation -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6" id="defense-tabs">
                <button onclick="showDefense('pqc', this)" class="defense-tab-btn flex-1 min-w-[150px] py-3 px-4 rounded-t-lg bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 font-bold tab-active">后量子密码 (PQC)</button>
                <button onclick="showDefense('qkd', this)" class="defense-tab-btn flex-1 min-w-[150px] py-3 px-4 rounded-t-lg bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-300">量子密钥分发 (QKD)</button>
                <button onclick="showDefense('qrng', this)" class="defense-tab-btn flex-1 min-w-[150px] py-3 px-4 rounded-t-lg bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-300">量子随机数 (QRNG)</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Content Areas -->
            <div class="glass-panel p-8 bg-white border-t-0 rounded-tl-none relative min-h-[400px]">
                
                <!-- PQC Content -->
                <div id="content-pqc" class="defense-content block animate-fade-in">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-3xl mr-4">💻</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">后量子密码 (Post-Quantum Cryptography)</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">安全范式：基于新型数学难题（如格密码、哈希签名），抵抗已知量子算法。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-emerald-700 border-b border-emerald-200 pb-2 mb-3">优势 (Pros)</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                                <li>➕ <strong>软件级平滑升级：</strong> 可直接运行在现有的互联网基础设施（路由器、光纤、移动网络）上，无需铺设新硬件。</li>
                                <li>➕ <strong>端到端兼容性：</strong> 完美支持公钥基础设施（PKI），解决身份认证和数字签名问题。</li>
                                <li>➕ <strong>成本极低：</strong> 部署成本仅为修改软件协议。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 border-b border-red-200 pb-2 mb-3">劣势与风险 (Cons)</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                                <li>➖ <strong>计算安全性：</strong> 并非绝对安全，理论上未来可能被新型经典数学算法或更强的量子算法攻破（如早期的SIKE算法被单核CPU攻破）。</li>
                                <li>➖ <strong>性能开销：</strong> 密钥尺寸和签名尺寸远大于RSA/ECC，增加网络带宽负担。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded border-l-4 border-slate-800">
                        <strong class="text-slate-900 block mb-1">🏛️ 国安局部署定性：</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">PQC应作为<strong>国家级广域网、政务外网和商用系统</strong>的绝对主力防御方案。必须采用“混合模式”（传统算法+PQC），并强调<strong>敏捷密码学</strong>（随时可热替换被攻破的算法）。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- QKD Content -->
                <div id="content-qkd" class="defense-content hidden animate-fade-in">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-3xl mr-4">📡</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">量子密钥分发 (Quantum Key Distribution)</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-600">安全范式：基于物理定律（量子不可克隆定理），窃听必定留下痕迹。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-emerald-700 border-b border-emerald-200 pb-2 mb-3">优势 (Pros)</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                                <li>➕ <strong>信息论安全：</strong> 提供绝对的安全密钥分发，防范“现在收集，未来解密”威胁。</li>
                                <li>➕ <strong>窃听感知：</strong> 任何中间人尝试测量量子态都会引发误码率上升，从而被合法通信方发现。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 border-b border-red-200 pb-2 mb-3">国家级部署瓶颈 (Cons)</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                                <li>➖ <strong>基建噩梦：</strong> 需要专用的暗光纤（不能与经典光网络混用）或卫星中继，成本极其高昂。</li>
                                <li>➖ <strong>距离限制与可信中继：</strong> 超过100公里衰减严重，必须依赖“可信中继站”。而在国安视角下，<strong>中继站本身就是巨大的单点被攻陷风险</strong>。</li>
                                <li>➖ <strong>无法解决认证：</strong> QKD仅分发对称密钥，防不了中间人伪装。它仍需依赖古典的PQC签名进行信道认证。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded border-l-4 border-purple-800">
                        <strong class="text-purple-900 block mb-1">🏛️ 国安局部署定性：</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-purple-800"><strong>拒绝大范围组网。</strong> QKD不适合作为通用互联网防御方案。仅限用于<strong>最高机密级别的点对点直连通信</strong>（如地下指挥所到核心数据中心的专线），且必须配合PQC进行信道认证。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- QRNG Content -->
                <div id="content-qrng" class="defense-content hidden animate-fade-in">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-3xl mr-4">🎲</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">量子随机数发生器 (Quantum Random Number Generator)</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-600">安全范式：利用量子叠加态或相位噪声等量子效应生成不可预测的真随机数。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-emerald-700 border-b border-emerald-200 pb-2 mb-3">优势 (Pros)</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                                <li>➕ <strong>绝对熵源：</strong> 彻底消除伪随机数发生器（PRNG）种子被推测的风险，从密码系统最源头保障安全。</li>
                                <li>➕ <strong>技术成熟且低成本：</strong> 芯片级QRNG已经商业化，可轻易集成到现有的服务器、HSM（硬件安全模块）甚至手机终端中。</li>
                                <li>➕ <strong>无基建要求：</strong> 不需要改变现有的网络传输架构。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-500 border-b border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-3">局限性 (Cons)</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                                <li>➖ <strong>只解决单点问题：</strong> QRNG只保证生成的密钥是安全的，无法保护密钥在网络中传输的过程，也不能抵御Shor算法对公钥体系的破解。必须与PQC或QKD结合使用。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 bg-teal-50 p-4 rounded border-l-4 border-teal-800">
                        <strong class="text-teal-900 block mb-1">🏛️ 国安局部署定性：</strong>
